{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":586,"text":"The will to live life differently can start"},{"time":3424,"text":"in some of the most unusual places."},{"time":6870,"text":"This is where I come from, Todmorden."},{"time":8816,"text":"It's a market town in the north of England,"},{"time":10836,"text":"15,000 people, between Leeds and Manchester,"},{"time":13507,"text":"fairly normal market town."},{"time":15580,"text":"It used to look like this,"},{"time":17750,"text":"and now it's more like this,"},{"time":20498,"text":"with fruit and veg and herbs sprouting up all over the place."},{"time":24223,"text":"We call it propaganda gardening. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28940,"text":"Corner row railway, station car park,"},{"time":31955,"text":"front of a health center, people's front gardens,"},{"time":35707,"text":"and even in front of the police station. (Laughter)"},{"time":39244,"text":"We've got edible canal towpaths,"},{"time":42234,"text":"and we've got sprouting cemeteries."},{"time":44400,"text":"The soil is extremely good. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50901,"text":"We've even invented a new form of tourism."},{"time":53144,"text":"It's called vegetable tourism, and believe it or not,"},{"time":56751,"text":"people come from all over the world to poke around in our raised beds,"},{"time":60675,"text":"even when there's not much growing. (Laughter)"},{"time":63659,"text":"But it starts a conversation. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":67289,"text":"And, you know, we're not doing it because we're bored. (Laughter)"},{"time":71297,"text":"We're doing it because we want to start a revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76114,"text":"We tried to answer this simple question:"},{"time":77432,"text":"Can you find a unifying language that cuts across age"},{"time":80322,"text":"and income and culture that will help people themselves"},{"time":84539,"text":"find a new way of living,"},{"time":86200,"text":"see spaces around them differently,"},{"time":88325,"text":"think about the resources they use differently,"},{"time":90928,"text":"interact differently?"},{"time":92921,"text":"Can we find that language?"},{"time":95290,"text":"And then, can we replicate those actions?"},{"time":99257,"text":"And the answer would appear to be yes,"},{"time":102015,"text":"and the language would appear to be food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105418,"text":"So, three and a half years ago, a few of us"},{"time":107437,"text":"sat around a kitchen table and"},{"time":109056,"text":"we just invented the whole thing. (Laughter)"},{"time":112424,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":115661,"text":"We came up with a really simple game plan that we put to a public meeting."},{"time":118252,"text":"We did not consult. We did not write a report."},{"time":120565,"text":"Enough of all that. (Laughter)"},{"time":123140,"text":"And we said to that public meeting in Todmorden,"},{"time":126158,"text":"look, let's imagine that our town"},{"time":129104,"text":"is focused around three plates:"},{"time":130860,"text":"a community plate, the way we live our everyday lives;"},{"time":133084,"text":"a learning plate, what we teach our kids in school"},{"time":136132,"text":"and what new skills we share amongst ourselves;"},{"time":138893,"text":"and business, what we do with the pound in our pocket"},{"time":142012,"text":"and which businesses we choose to support."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143833,"text":"Now, let's imagine those plates agitated"},{"time":146640,"text":"with community actions around food."},{"time":149280,"text":"If we start one of those community plates spinning,"},{"time":151521,"text":"that's really great, that really starts to empower people,"},{"time":154905,"text":"but if we can then spin that community plate"},{"time":156992,"text":"with the learning plate, and then spin it with the business plate,"},{"time":159888,"text":"we've got a real show there, we've got some action theater."},{"time":163624,"text":"We're starting to build resilience ourselves."},{"time":166969,"text":"We're starting to reinvent community ourselves,"},{"time":170360,"text":"and we've done it all without a flipping strategy document."},{"time":173827,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179138,"text":"And here's the thing as well."},{"time":181930,"text":"We've not asked anybody's permission to do this,"},{"time":184346,"text":"we're just doing it. (Laughter)"},{"time":186639,"text":"And we are certainly not waiting for that check"},{"time":188400,"text":"to drop through the letterbox before we start,"},{"time":191138,"text":"and most importantly of all, we are not daunted"},{"time":193470,"text":"by the sophisticated arguments that say,"},{"time":195322,"text":"\"These small actions are meaningless in the face of tomorrow's problems,\""},{"time":199218,"text":"because I have seen the power of small actions,"},{"time":202886,"text":"and it is awesome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204957,"text":"So, back to the public meeting. (Laughter)"},{"time":208070,"text":"We put that proposition to the meeting, two seconds,"},{"time":210959,"text":"and then the room exploded."},{"time":212667,"text":"I have never, ever experienced anything like that in my life."},{"time":216555,"text":"And it's been the same in every single room, in every town"},{"time":219937,"text":"that we've ever told our story."},{"time":221492,"text":"People are ready and respond to the story of food."},{"time":225836,"text":"They want positive actions they can engage in,"},{"time":228093,"text":"and in their bones, they know it's time"},{"time":230692,"text":"to take personal responsibility"},{"time":232581,"text":"and invest in more kindness to each other"},{"time":235152,"text":"and to the environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238075,"text":"And since we had that meeting three and a half years ago,"},{"time":241389,"text":"it's been a heck of a roller coaster."},{"time":244639,"text":"We started with a seed swap, really simple stuff,"},{"time":247535,"text":"and then we took an area of land, a strip on the side"},{"time":249784,"text":"of our main road, which was a dog toilet, basically,"},{"time":252286,"text":"and we turned it into a really lovely herb garden."},{"time":255640,"text":"We took the corner of the car park in the station"},{"time":257926,"text":"that you saw, and we made vegetable beds"},{"time":259661,"text":"for everybody to share and pick from themselves."},{"time":263185,"text":"We went to the doctors. We've just had"},{"time":264494,"text":"a 6-million-pound health center built in Todmorden,"},{"time":267399,"text":"and for some reason that I cannot comprehend,"},{"time":270087,"text":"it has been surrounded by prickly plants. (Laughter)"},{"time":273880,"text":"So we went to the doctors, said, \"Would you mind us taking them up?\""},{"time":276969,"text":"They said, \"Absolutely fine, provided you get planning permission"},{"time":279323,"text":"and you do it in Latin and you do it in triplicate,\""},{"time":281245,"text":"so we did — (Laughter) — and now there are fruit trees"},{"time":284035,"text":"and bushes and herbs and vegetables"},{"time":287330,"text":"around that doctor's surgery."},{"time":290560,"text":"And there's been lots of other examples, like the corn"},{"time":292836,"text":"that was in front of the police station,"},{"time":294692,"text":"and the old people's home that we've planted it with food"},{"time":296509,"text":"that they can pick and grow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298481,"text":"But it isn't just about growing,"},{"time":300191,"text":"because we all are part of this jigsaw."},{"time":302736,"text":"It's about taking those artistic people in your community"},{"time":305610,"text":"and doing some fabulous designs in those raised beds"},{"time":307843,"text":"to explain to people what's growing there,"},{"time":309914,"text":"because there's so many people that don't really recognize"},{"time":312130,"text":"a vegetable unless it's in a bit of plastic"},{"time":314018,"text":"with a bit of an instruction packet on the top. (Laughter)"},{"time":316090,"text":"So we have some people who designed these things,"},{"time":318986,"text":"\"If it looks like this, please don't pick it, but if it looks like this,"},{"time":321003,"text":"help yourself.\""},{"time":322980,"text":"This is about sharing and investing in kindness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325849,"text":"And for those people that don't want to do either"},{"time":327706,"text":"of those things, maybe they can cook,"},{"time":329705,"text":"so we pick them seasonally and then we go on the street,"},{"time":332578,"text":"or in the pub, or in the church,"},{"time":334811,"text":"or wherever people are living their lives."},{"time":336443,"text":"This is about us going to the people and saying,"},{"time":338985,"text":"\"We are all part of the local food jigsaw,"},{"time":341394,"text":"we are all part of a solution.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":344049,"text":"And then, because we know we've got vegetable tourists"},{"time":346265,"text":"and we love them to bits and they're absolutely fantastic,"},{"time":348973,"text":"we thought, what could we do to give them an even better experience?"},{"time":351549,"text":"So we invented, without asking, of course,"},{"time":353953,"text":"the Incredible Edible Green Route."},{"time":356059,"text":"And this is a route of exhibition gardens,"},{"time":358784,"text":"and edible towpaths, and bee-friendly sites, and the story"},{"time":363495,"text":"of pollinators, and it's a route that we designed"},{"time":366363,"text":"that takes people through the whole of our town,"},{"time":368969,"text":"past our cafes and our small shops, through our market,"},{"time":372188,"text":"not just to and fro from the supermarket,"},{"time":375601,"text":"and we're hoping that, in changing people's footfall"},{"time":377899,"text":"around our town, we're also changing their behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380754,"text":"And then there's the second plate, the learning plate."},{"time":384474,"text":"Well, we're in partnership with a high school."},{"time":386054,"text":"We've created a company. We are designing and building"},{"time":389127,"text":"an aquaponics unit in some land that was spare"},{"time":391175,"text":"at the back of the high school, like you do,"},{"time":393082,"text":"and now we're going to be growing fish and vegetables"},{"time":395275,"text":"in an orchard with bees,"},{"time":397824,"text":"and the kids are helping us build that,"},{"time":400082,"text":"and the kids are on the board, and because the community"},{"time":402895,"text":"was really keen on working with the high school,"},{"time":404427,"text":"the high school is now teaching agriculture,"},{"time":407795,"text":"and because it's teaching agriculture, we started to think,"},{"time":410911,"text":"how could we then get those kids that never had a qualification"},{"time":413694,"text":"before in their lives but are really excited about growing,"},{"time":416245,"text":"how can we give them some more experience?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417949,"text":"So we got some land that was donated"},{"time":419908,"text":"by a local garden center."},{"time":421166,"text":"It was really quite muddy, but in a truly incredible way,"},{"time":424500,"text":"totally voluntary-led, we have turned that"},{"time":427110,"text":"into a market garden training center,"},{"time":429307,"text":"and that is polytunnels and raised beds"},{"time":432271,"text":"and all the things you need to get the soil under your fingers"},{"time":434975,"text":"and think maybe there's a job in this for me in the future."},{"time":437296,"text":"And because we were doing that, some local academics said,"},{"time":439504,"text":"\"You know, we could help design"},{"time":440836,"text":"a commercial horticulture course for you."},{"time":442608,"text":"There's not one that we know of.\""},{"time":444003,"text":"So they're doing that, and we're going to launch it later this year,"},{"time":446647,"text":"and it's all an experiment, and it's all voluntary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449232,"text":"And then there's the third plate,"},{"time":450851,"text":"because if you walk through an edible landscape,"},{"time":452669,"text":"and if you're learning new skills, and if you start to get"},{"time":455264,"text":"interested in what's growing seasonally,"},{"time":457312,"text":"you might just want to spend more of your own money"},{"time":459224,"text":"in support of local producers,"},{"time":461304,"text":"not just veg, but meat and cheese and beer"},{"time":463056,"text":"and whatever else it might be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465135,"text":"But then, we're just a community group, you know."},{"time":467872,"text":"We're just all volunteers. What could we actually do?"},{"time":469830,"text":"So we did some really simple things."},{"time":471580,"text":"We fundraised, we got some blackboards,"},{"time":473367,"text":"we put \"Incredible Edible\" on the top,"},{"time":474537,"text":"we gave it every market trader that was selling locally,"},{"time":476713,"text":"and they scribbled on what they were selling in any one week."},{"time":479640,"text":"Really popular. People congregated around it."},{"time":482096,"text":"Sales were up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483744,"text":"And then, we had a chat with the farmers, and we said,"},{"time":486740,"text":"\"We're really serious about this,\""},{"time":487717,"text":"but they didn't actually believe us, so we thought,"},{"time":490135,"text":"okay, what should we do? I know. If we can create"},{"time":492760,"text":"a campaign around one product and show them"},{"time":495334,"text":"there is local loyalty to that product,"},{"time":497377,"text":"maybe they'll change their mind and see we're serious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499720,"text":"So we launched a campaign -- because it just amuses me --"},{"time":502711,"text":"called Every Egg Matters. (Laughter)"},{"time":504784,"text":"And what we did was we put people on our egg map."},{"time":508405,"text":"It's a stylized map of Togmorden."},{"time":510556,"text":"Anybody that's selling their excess eggs"},{"time":512195,"text":"at the garden gate, perfectly legally, to their neighbors,"},{"time":514733,"text":"we've stuck on there. We started with four,"},{"time":517150,"text":"and we've now got 64 on, and the result of that was"},{"time":519424,"text":"that people were then going into shops"},{"time":520924,"text":"asking for a local Todmorden egg, and the result of that"},{"time":523605,"text":"was, some farmers upped the amount of flocks they got"},{"time":525894,"text":"of free range birds, and then they went on to meat birds,"},{"time":528003,"text":"and although these are really, really small steps,"},{"time":530584,"text":"that increasing local economic confidence"},{"time":535273,"text":"is starting to play out in a number of ways,"},{"time":537850,"text":"and we now have farmers doing cheese"},{"time":539152,"text":"and they've upped their flocks and rare breed pigs,"},{"time":540941,"text":"they're doing pasties and pies and things"},{"time":542349,"text":"that they would have never done before."},{"time":544722,"text":"We've got increasing market stalls selling local food,"},{"time":547343,"text":"and in a survey that local students did for us, 49 percent"},{"time":551557,"text":"of all food traders in that town said that their bottom line"},{"time":554510,"text":"had increased because of what we were actually doing."},{"time":556916,"text":"And we're just volunteers and it's only an experiment."},{"time":560006,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":561410,"text":"Now, none of this is rocket science."},{"time":563820,"text":"It certainly is not clever, and it's not original."},{"time":566699,"text":"But it is joined up, and it is inclusive."},{"time":570506,"text":"This is not a movement for those people"},{"time":572629,"text":"that are going to sort themselves out anyway."},{"time":574551,"text":"This is a movement for everyone."},{"time":577447,"text":"We have a motto: If you eat, you're in. (Laughter)"},{"time":581313,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":587402,"text":"Across age, across income, across culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592479,"text":"It's been really quite a roller coaster experience,"},{"time":596086,"text":"but going back to that first question that we asked,"},{"time":598559,"text":"is it replicable? Yeah. It most certainly is replicable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601818,"text":"More than 30 towns in England now are spinning"},{"time":604632,"text":"the Incredible Edible plate."},{"time":606760,"text":"Whichever way they want to do it, of their own volition,"},{"time":610255,"text":"they're trying to make their own lives differently,"},{"time":612949,"text":"and worldwide, we've got communities across America"},{"time":615697,"text":"and Japan -- it's incredible, isn't it? I mean,"},{"time":617441,"text":"America and Japan and New Zealand."},{"time":619956,"text":"People after the earthquake in New Zealand visited us"},{"time":622480,"text":"in order to incorporate some of this public spiritedness"},{"time":625531,"text":"around local growing into the heart of Christchurch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630183,"text":"And none of this takes more money"},{"time":633030,"text":"and none of this demands a bureaucracy,"},{"time":636157,"text":"but it does demand that you think things differently"},{"time":639020,"text":"and you are prepared to bend budgets and work programs"},{"time":642717,"text":"in order to create that supportive framework"},{"time":644845,"text":"that communities can bounce off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647559,"text":"And there's some great ideas already in our patch."},{"time":650475,"text":"Our local authority has decided to make everywhere"},{"time":653259,"text":"Incredible Edible, and in support of that"},{"time":655921,"text":"have decided to do two things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657406,"text":"First, they're going to create an asset register of spare land"},{"time":660515,"text":"that they've got, put it in a food bank so that communities"},{"time":662746,"text":"can use that wherever they live,"},{"time":664482,"text":"and they're going to underpin that with a license."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666659,"text":"And then they've said to every single one of their workforce,"},{"time":669040,"text":"if you can, help those communities grow,"},{"time":671537,"text":"and help them to maintain their spaces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673650,"text":"Suddenly, we're seeing actions on the ground"},{"time":675689,"text":"from local government. We're seeing this mainstreamed."},{"time":677969,"text":"We are responding creatively at last to what Rio demanded"},{"time":682394,"text":"of us, and there's lots more you could do."},{"time":684573,"text":"I mean, just to list a few. One, please stop putting"},{"time":686933,"text":"prickly plants around public buildings. It's a waste of space."},{"time":690301,"text":"(Laughter) Secondly, please create -- please, please create"},{"time":693703,"text":"edible landscapes so that our children start to walk"},{"time":696482,"text":"past their food day in, day out, on our high streets,"},{"time":698665,"text":"in our parks, wherever that might be."},{"time":701251,"text":"Inspire local planners to put the food sites at the heart"},{"time":704945,"text":"of the town and the city plan, not relegate them"},{"time":708208,"text":"to the edges of the settlements that nobody can see."},{"time":711528,"text":"Encourage all our schools to take this seriously."},{"time":714345,"text":"This isn't a second class exercise."},{"time":716578,"text":"If we want to inspire the farmers of tomorrow,"},{"time":719546,"text":"then please let us say to every school,"},{"time":722595,"text":"create a sense of purpose around the importance"},{"time":726575,"text":"to the environment, local food and soils."},{"time":729375,"text":"Put that at the heart of your school culture,"},{"time":731262,"text":"and you will create a different generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734424,"text":"There are so many things you can do, but ultimately"},{"time":736863,"text":"this is about something really simple."},{"time":739151,"text":"Through an organic process, through"},{"time":742776,"text":"an increasing recognition of the power of small actions,"},{"time":747063,"text":"we are starting, at last, to believe in ourselves again,"},{"time":750888,"text":"and to believe in our capacity, each and every one of us,"},{"time":754729,"text":"to build a different and a kinder future,"},{"time":759122,"text":"and in my book, that's incredible."},{"time":761545,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":765410,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":775902,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}